Author
Author is an interface that represents an author with a full name and a citation name.

This class represents a book, which is a type of publication.

This class represents an individual author.
InstitutionalAuthor
This class represents an institutional author.
JournalArticle
This class represents a journal article, which is a type of publication.
Publication
This class represents a generic publication.
PublicationMain
The PublicationMain class demonstrates the use of the Author, IndividualAuthor, Book, JournalArticle, and WebPage classes.
PublicationTest
The PublicationTest class contains unit tests for the Book, JournalArticle, and WebPage classes to ensure their Harvard reference formatting is correct.

The WebPage class extends the Publication class
